README FILE:

Toggling some features:

'r' turns rain off/on
'b' changes rain particles to a quad
'l' shows a raindrop model at the starting corner of the map
'=' speeds up rain
'-' slows down rain
'f' pauses rain
't' turns on torch and enables nightmode
'g' enables the movement of the sun
'c' changes camera mode between first person, third person and free view mode

Camera movements:

'a' strafe left
's / down arrow' walk backwards
'w / up arrow' walk forwards
'd' strafe right
'left arrow' rotate view left
'right arrow' rotate view right

in free view mode, shift and ctrl will raise and lower the camera (along y axis)
you can also fly off the map and through the terrain